!<mpls-tp-oam>
mpls-tp oam
  pw pw221
    meg 60076
      oam enable
      meg-id 584398333
      local-mep 1 type bidirectional
      peer-mep 2 type bidirectional
    $
  $
  pw pw222
    meg 36745
      oam enable
